description: This file contains implementation code for the Slap Owo Uoac Object, specifically the function SlapOwoUoacReset which resets the object state by cleaning internal tables and resetting superclass components. It is part of the SLAP (Service Logic Aggregation Plane) framework in the broader RDK Management system.

methods.name: ANSC_STATUS SlapOwoUoacReset(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject)
methods.description: Resets the internal state of the Slap Owo Uoac Object by cleaning its internal table and resetting superclass states.
